Hacker of the Year,title="image"]

Joe Julian (pictured at home) is the Sr. Systems Administrator for
http://www.edwyse.com[Ed Wyse Beauty Supply]. Managing 27 locations
across 3 states, Ed Wyse strives to meet their customers expectations
100% of the time with the best system availability in the industry.

GlusterFS helps us meet that expectation by reducing our exposure to
single points of failure by spreading our file availability across a
triple redundancy pool of servers as well as disks.

Joe is well known to the IRC crowd, formerly as EdWyse and now as
JoeJulian he and several other dedicated community members help users in
the #gluster channel on freenode.
